attr.title: Self
attr.desc: Who are you? A short game about a lost soul. Recover the fragments of your SELF. Be touched by the higher being.
attr.inst: Download the game free at itch.io (https://klardonics.itch.io/overbowed). Download, extract, and copy the game files into self/assets
